  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency compression to v1.7.1",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/expressjs/compression\">compression</a> from <code>v1.7.0</code> to <code>v1.7.1</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>expressjs/compression</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"171\">1.7.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/expressjs/compression/commit/93586e75a0a1c5bbfd353c4cec1cfcee2e52adde\"><code>93586e7</code></a> 1.7.1</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/expressjs/compression/commit/bd3fa8a80addbbc227bcaa5929a4373d76676a4b\"><code>bd3fa8a</code></a> deps: bytes@3.0.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/expressjs/compression/commit/e1ce980407814dca14c76cdd4e4aee61b56e4caa\"><code>e1ce980</code></a> deps: vary@~1.1.2</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/expressjs/compression/commit/d0f7eab38f40e3bac0a4d32489a6b9accc0820fe\"><code>d0f7eab</code></a> deps: debug@2.6.9</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/expressjs/compression/commit/931c3469a41205794cadf980967dabc40fe4c1d4\"><code>931c346</code></a> build: Node.js@8.4</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/expressjs/compression/commit/8c8e36ab3196df83d2d89cd26936b6e7b4c368aa\"><code>8c8e36a</code></a> deps: compressible@~2.0.11</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/expressjs/compression/commit/8a5e773aa9d4e27a3109bc7870e3582505c19eb9\"><code>8a5e773</code></a> deps: accepts@~1.3.4</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/expressjs/compression/commit/7b4a7e28bb5f37db5c1aa7fa6f60b2191588c275\"><code>7b4a7e2</code></a> build: eslint-plugin-node@5.1.1</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/expressjs/compression/commit/de30e3a3511544204060c8375183f322e50d2d24\"><code>de30e3a</code></a> build: mocha@2.5.3</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
